{"tid":1320130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(義士醫生) 陳沛然: 若示威繼續武力升級, 只會令更多義士犧牲, 政府卻完全不會理會","createTime":"2019-07-15T10:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T01:02:15.000Z","uid":134071,"like":145,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"adfbe45974aa8db6be4603d10adbc205eb63db3a","tid":1320130,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:12:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2394511030822946&amp;id=2236059276668123\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2394511030822946%26id%3D2236059276668123&d=mMU56kjTNdUxye0JV9HIjXlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=d93bfa41\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2394511030822946&amp;id=2236059276668123</a><br />\n<br />\n陳沛然醫生議員<br />\n<br />\n求求大家，不要將武力或行動繼續升級，那些高層和管理層只會袖手旁觀，或在冷氣房提出譴責，他們不會企出來解決問題。近來每逢大型活動，首先和平遊行，然後少部份人及警察留下，對峙對罵，最後武力清場，雙方受傷。<strong>我不想見到有人再犧牲生命，在外圍救人時，眼淚在心裡流。</strong><br />\n<br />\n4 小時 &middot; 公開"},{"pid":"de0afb641824fe01997f76a1ce9bccd38627518e","tid":1320130,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:15:04.000Z","msg":"【我冇嘢講2.0】有人冒警！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319116\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319116</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警！\n你扮警察\n涉嫌冒警及傷人\n涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"a24370d729b93af3c64964ffacec5df9615b5ba4","tid":1320130,"uid":134071,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:15:33.000Z","msg":"陳沛然醫生係抗爭前線做救護, 明白義士既感受 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"108b5d9756fac3c3a97bb3071882514f3250adb7","tid":1320130,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:17:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ed049202d5b57c94e3055566975ad32545aa3e","tid":1320130,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"re