平，係5:00既時候警方無故主動挑機在先<br />\n2. 6點幾無神神係禾輋出防暴隊推進，個段時間正值繁忙時段，有乜理由推進？而且係多方同時推，得一條路可以走。<br />\n3. 好喇，點解釋九點幾既時候 火車站同埋其他商場同一時間有咁多警察阻止市民出去？<br />\n<br />\n無人想升級，無人想去到呢步。問題由邊個造成？<br />\n<br />\n好喇，加多一句真係停<br />\n尋晚，有個年青人係急救站痛哭段片，試問點解警方又唔比在場急救義工去救人？<br />\n4 小時前<br />\n<br />\n<strong>陳沛然醫生議員<br />\n我在現場，見到前因後果。<br />\n 4 小時前</strong>"},{"pid":"462f8b28aa460144865f54091943e94746c5645c","tid":1320130,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e7abf7f6d6d0e0b4c6b299c43b6ec5350f7fa2f","tid":1320130,"uid":49563,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:29:19.000Z","msg":"睇真啲<br />\n人哋唔係講俾示威者聽㗎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:31:43.000Z","msg":"佢係講俾示威者聽<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>求求大家，不要將武力或行動繼續升級</strong></em>"},{"pid":"a5bbeb229ab7cdfd9b0414bef1a57b96539ccff6","tid":1320130,"uid":247845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:31:43.000Z","msg":"班高層係涼冷氣 但係班狗死要出黎同市民對抗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無解"},{"pid":"c83554df000eaa6673b5025823e95e3564c5c55e","tid":1320130,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a5bbeb229ab7cdfd9b0414bef1a57b96539ccff6","tid":1320130,"uid":247845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:31:43.000Z","msg":"班高層係涼冷氣 但係班狗死要出黎同市民對抗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無解"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:34:39.000Z","msg":"(D100) 警員家屬訪問: 政府期待前線警察死亡. 香港示威者不要中政府的計.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tgEWX1gh-Lo&amp;t=3s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtgEWX1gh-Lo%26t%3D3s&d=mMU56kjTNdUxye0JV9HIjXlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=14996397\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tgEWX1gh-Lo&amp;t=3s</a>"},{"pid":"30403d5784094dd5f04572f897759efe5a3439ee","tid":1320130,"uid":212646,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:34:52.000Z","msg":"我會無時無刻一得閒就推呢個po